title: S+ Jinx??!?!
body:
So I main Jinx, and I've just been wondering how to get the S+ rank with her?

Some games i'll go with no deaths, good kills/assists and a high creep kill and still wont get that S+ rank. :(
I know it depends on a ton of stuff but just wondering what the criteria is for Jinx specifically. 

Have a photo reference!

replies.body:
If you have really high kill participation/cs/everything really
You get s+
I've gotten s+ going 5-0-8 just because my team's total kills was 14
